txAMQP 0.3:

- Added support for hearbeat (Anthony Lenton)
- Added support for setuptools (Zooko Wilcox-O'Hearn)
- Added support for loading the XML spec from a string (Zooko Wilcox-O'Hearn)
- Added support for multiple brokers in the testsuite (Thomas Hervé)
- Added support for basic_return
- Added support for detecting closed connections
- Fixed reference cycle error (Dan Di Spaltro)
- Fixed closed queue errors in the Thrift glue (Jonathan Stoppani)
- Fixed frame decoding errors
- Updated support for Thrift

Dan Di Spaltro and Thomas Hervé became committers.
